name: Kelly Walsh High School
directions: Located in corridor just west of the large stairway in the commons area on lowest floor.  Near loading dock area and gymnasium
comment: (2) Single occupancy staff bathrooms.  Recommend inquiring with school staff/event organizers in advance of attending event where access is needed to make sure they will be unlocked and available for the specific time and date.

name: San Diego international airport
directions: By security for gates 3-18.
comment: Outside of security so no ticket needed. Right inside the southwest entrance.

name: Natrona County High School
directions: Located in corridor adjoining main floor lobby/commons area, turn right at exit of auditorium lobby, go down hall and take first left.  Go all the way down corridor, look for staff bathroom on left hand side near vending machines.
comment: Single occupancy staff bathroom, normally locked and requires custodial staff to unlock and block door open.  Arrangements have been made for this bathroom to be available during symphony concerts and ARTCORE perfromances being hosted in the school auditorium.  Recommend inquiring with school staff and/or partner organization(s) prior to attending other events hosted on campus to make sure they know the single occupancy bathroom is needed by a patron for a specific date/time/event.

name: Casper Events Center
directions: Located inside first aid station near box office in southwest corner on main floor concourse
comment: Single occupancy bathroom within secured area used as a first aid station during shows and events.  Recommend notifying security/box office staff prior to attending event in which access to this bathroom is desired to expedite access during event - traffic flow, venue logistics and specific security measures vary event to event so be sure to plan ahead.   Staff have been understanding and accommodating towards transgender and non-binary identifying patrons who are not comfortable using the regular restroom facilities by providing them access to this area.

name: Chelsea District Library

name: First Interstate Bank downtown Casper branch

name: Casper Recreation Center
directions: Part of swimming pool area locker rooms between main lobby and pool.  Located on each side of corridor.
comment: (2) large gender neutral/family dressing rooms with locking doors each complete with single restroom and shower, benches, etc for paid member/guest and student use.  Lockers provided in corridor itself.  Inquire with front desk staff for after-hours access if taking evening classes that extend past pool hours.

name: Tuco's Taco Lounge
directions: Two gender neutral washrooms, beside dining area.
comment: I believe it is for paying customers only.

name: Wheeler Hall/Music building
directions: Located in south west corner of the 2nd floor lobby near entryway.  Look for music building "MU" on campus map, building is adjacent to the north of the Gertrude Krampert theatre complex.
comment: (2) Single occupancy restrooms available during building open hours.  These are the closest gender neutral/single occupancy bathrooms to the Krampert theatre complex that can be readily accessed by the general public and theatre patrons before/after shows and during intermissions.  Exit the main lobby by the box office, walk outside and across a short sidewalk to the large glass doors into the upper floor of the music building
